reneshakil, it did that to me yesterday, but only once. i think the captcha thing is messed up. heck, last week, every time i posted, i received an error message. BUT the torrent went live after a few minutes without any further action from me, so it worked out in the end. VERY, VERY frustrating, i know. hang in there my friend. thanks again for your efforts!

just to update: i've d/l'ed noble causes and image united 1. #2 i'm having trouble with. will torrent them when i get it.
I left a comment in your Image torrent. I went ahead and got those comics in print today. Thank you for looking for them. Maybe others might want them. I can torrent Image United #3 if you want.

Well I just looked and Image United #3 is on TPB and downloadable. Guess I won't upload it then. Thanks again for taking time to find them. Just went to get some comics from Wednesday and went into back issue bins and grabbed those.
